headline: New industrial development worth $7.7B for Norfolk Southern in 2025
summary: Norfolk Southern said its customers advanced dozens of industrial projects representing $7.7 billion worth of investment in new or expanded rail-served facilities in 2025. The post New industrial development worth $7.7B for Norfolk Southern in 2025 appeared first on FreightWaves.

headline: 1 Cash-Producing Stock to Keep an Eye On and 2 We Find Risky
summary: While strong cash flow is a key indicator of stability, it doesn’t always translate to superior returns. Some cash-heavy businesses struggle with inefficient spending, slowing demand, or weak competitive positioning.
